description: This week we present Tyson, a tall dark haired college guy from Washington.He replied to one of our online ads for talent, so we brought him to us. He told us that he works at a local pizza parlor and attends Washington State, where he is studying architectural design. Well, he won't need all that brain power to put on a good show, but it doesn't hurt, does it? This stud was eager to show us what he had and we can see why.He strokes himself on the couch, washes up in the shower, and then finishes himself off on the bed, where he UNLOADS onto himself. Yes, 'unloads' deserves the CAPS. You'll see what I mean...ENJOY!
title: Tyson
